title: The.Face.UK.S01E07.WEB-DLx264.JIVE.mp4
description: The action moves to Paris, where Caroline Winberg explains that come rain or shine, the hopefuls must remain composed on location, and gives them a masterclass in dealing with the elements. They then get the chance to put their new-found knowledge to use on a shoot for French designer Longchamp along the banks of the Seine - but a twist in the proceedings calls time on team loyalties, and the line-up for next week's final is decided.
